                <p align="center">
                    <STRONG><u>ADDENDUM</u></STRONG>
                </p>
                <p>This addendum agreement
                    <STRONG>("Agreement")</STRONG> is made at Gurgaon on <strong>&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,MM'/'dd'/'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /></apex:outputText></strong> ("Effective Date") by and between:</p>
                <p><strong>{!accObj.Legal_Name__c}</strong> a ({!accObj.Business_Entity__r.Name}) having its registered office at &nbsp;
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.Address_Line__c!=null && regParentAddress.Address_Line__c!='', regParentAddress.Address_Line__c + ', ', null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.City__c!=null && regParentAddress.City__c!='', regParentAddress.City__c + ', ', null)}"/>
